Package lubiku.castleQuest.Configuration

Class Configurator

java.lang.Object
lubiku.castleQuest.Configuration.Configurator
public class Configurator extends Object

Configurator

The Configurator class is responsible for loading and managing various configurations used in the game. It uses the Gson library for reading and parsing JSON configuration files.
